message.entry: The factor does not contain the specified node ID.
Rows of the node ID matrix specified during factor construction must contain unique entries.
Accelerometer and gyroscope readings must be of equal size.
The second argument must be a 3-by-3 or 3-by-3-by-N camera intrinsic matrix.
Computer Vision Toolbox license is required to use ''factorCameraSE3AndPointXYZ''.
Pose scale component in SIM(3) factor measurement must be greater than 0.
ids input to ''factorCameraSE3AndPointXYZ'' must have 2 or 3 column.
The specified SensorTransform is ignored since sensor transform ID is specified as third column in ids input.
